Included here are:
phpflickr:	php wrapper for flickr API including their unique auth scheme
		svn export http://code.google.com/p/phpflickr/

php-sdk:	this is the Facebook sdk which includes oAuth2.0 for facebook
		git pull https://github.com/facebook/php-sdk/

tmhOAuth:	the twitter oAuth 1.1a class by themattharris
		git pull https://github.com/themattharris/tmhOAuth

twitteroauth:	a second twitter oAuth1.1a class by "abraham"
		git pull https://github.com/abraham/twitteroauth

One could use the Zend sauth lib to replace all of these (and more, its nice!)... but who wants to use Zend? For those who do, see https://github.com/nnixaa/sauth
